Name: Silence of the Nativity
Description: The Nativity has been dark since you awoke. Those of the crew that witnessed the sorrow-spiders' rage will not speak of it. Pressed, they only repeat, "Not now. Please."

DefaultEvent.Name: A time as far in the future as possible
DefaultEvent.Description: Should you return to this accursed place at all.

ChildBranches.Name: There is a raw, broken certainty in their voices
ChildBranches.Description: Let it be a matter for another time then.
